      <title>向女性支付 18 美元如何赢得印度选举</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/opinion/articles/2024-11-25/india-election-how-paying-women-18-won-maharashtra-poll</link>
      <description><![CDATA[莫迪领导的政党通过向女性选民支付小额补助，在印度最富裕的州之一提振了其低迷的财富。在日益扩大的不平等现象中，这一策略的吸引力正在不断扩大。    ]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/opinion/articles/2024-11-25/india-election-how-paying-women-18-won-maharashtra-poll</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 25 Nov 2024 03:14:41 GMT</pubDate>
